### Welcome to the page.
eQualityCoin is a price-stable iteration of bitcoin based on work by @mprestonsparks at www.equalitycoin.io 

We'd appreciate if you'd check out the code and site. 

If you have any feedback you'd like to share, please contact us via the website.
